In resources setup page it is defined:

* The absence reporting job – Absence Job No.

* If absence hours need to be approved or not

The boolean “Hide Absence Job No. on TS" and "Insert TS Absences on appr." work together: their activation blocks the reporting of hours on the absence job through the time sheet. It becomes mandatory for all resources to follow the approval workflow:

